159
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,270
The reason I don't date

160
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,330
is for the other person's sake.

161
00:07:15,450 --> 00:07:16,890
I need to preserve

162
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,160
my Pure Yang Sacred Body.

163
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:18,690
Besides,

164
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,720
love is just a false concept.

165
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,360
Living things reproduce.

166
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,950
Once they reach sexual maturity

167
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,800
and encounter a suitable mate,

168
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,240
their brains start producing

169
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,240
