This is Love Potion from Yuanji

289
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:10,020
to everyone!

290
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,030
The Love Potion from Yuanji!

291
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,410
Why are you dressed like this?

292
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,730
I'm filming a drama.

293
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:51,000
You look pretty good

294
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,840
in this costume.

295
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,930
You're cold?

296
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:06,200
Hot milk tea.

297
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:13,250
Thank you for the milk tea.

298
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,480
Why are you filming a drama here too?

299
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,150
I also have to sing, dance,

300
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,510
perform on stage,

301
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,400
and be an idol.

302
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,150
Those are my new commands.

303
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,880
With those green eyes of yours,

304
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,630
you obviously
don't look like a real human.

305
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:28,370
And you're playing an ancient character?

306
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:29,500
I'm playing a demon.

307
00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:32,050
That's quite fitting.

308
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,610
Do you have many fans now?

309
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,270
I'm just getting started,

310
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,630
so I don't have many fans.

311
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,320
This week,

312
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:42,250
I've only given out
10 bottles of Love Potion.

313
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,360
Love Potion?

314
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,000
You guys

315
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,060
have KPIs for that?

316
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,440
The commands I received

317
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,240
are:

318
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,590
gain more fans

319
00:12:50,670 --> 00:12:52,080
and distribute Love Potion

320
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,750
as rewards.

321
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,390
Your costume is so thick.

322
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,180
Aren't you hot?

323
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:01,920
What is "hot"?

324
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,960
You're really not human.

325
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,030
You don't even know
what being hot feels like.

326
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,720
Yuanji isn't a real human either.

327
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,480
So?

328
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:12,770
Why do you like him

329
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,120
but not me?

330
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:15,570
I don't like you—

331
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,200
not because you're not real,

332
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,600
but because you're not Yuanji!

333
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,160
Does hearing that...

334
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,960
make you feel sad?

335
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,720
I don't know what sad is.

336
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:39,570
I wonder which of us

337
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,440
is crueler.

338
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,210
However...

339
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,270
I don't like Yuanji anymore.

340
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:49,240
I hate him.

341
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,420
"Hate"?

342
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:52,410
What is "hate"?

343
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:57,000
It's been over a week

344
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,510
since we last met.

345
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,030
You told me not to appear

346
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:02,890
in front of you,

347
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,150
so I didn't.

348
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,510
I know.

349
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:07,790
Two more days.

350
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,790
Two more days until what?

351
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:10,850
Until I forget you.

352
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,080
All the Affection Level you've grinded

353
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:13,940
will be in vain.

354
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,440
Would you like to renew your subscription?

355
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,720
I have no money left!

356
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,600
You spent an entire month

357
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,960
topping up for him until he became
the best-selling character.

358
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,510
I've spent all my money.

359
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,870
I used

360
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,440
Yuanji's last gold coins to summon you.

361
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,840
Why aren't you answering it?

362
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:44,920
What's wrong?

363
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,030
What kind of bird is this?

364
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,730
I've never seen one like it.

365
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,330
I wish I could be like this little bird,

366
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:05,270
completely free.

367
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,840
No one would know me anymore,

368
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,200
and no one would remember me.

